Customer Governance/Policy Guidance Initial Outline:
- Operational Security
     -Incident Identification & Tracking
     -vulnerability accessment
     -effective response

- Guideline/Process Compliance 
     -core process required for all divisions 
     -validation of best devops internal practices implemented 
     -implementation of real-time dashboard statistics

- Risk Assessment
     -defines prioritization based on risk
     -consistent implementation of risk mitigation methods
     -defined streamlined standard deployment 
     -defined emergency response

- Audit & Monitoring
     -Real-time dashboard & monitoring capabilities:
       -type/category of incidents 
       -success validation of resolutions 
       -rate of incidents per function or service provider
